Add.key: Server side command visibility condition for Licenses command. This command should be visible for Teamcenter Version <=11.2.3. It should be visible only if selected object is of type WorkspaceObject, Dataset or Form. It should not be visible if selected object is of type EPMTask or Signoff. It should be visible if the logged in user is a member of dba group or is in the ITAR Admin or IP Admin role.
